\b \cf2 Slide 9
\b0 \
The purpose of the bias rating is not to tell the reader whether a story is accurate or fake news, but to provide the user with information pertaining to where the story originated while also providing additional stories on the same subject from an\'a0\cf3 (click)\cf2  alternate source. It encourages the reader to view information from a\'a0\cf3 (click)\cf2  different perspective and, ultimately, be\'a0\cf3 (click)\cf2  better informed.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl216\partightenfactor0
